Package: upowertray
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lightweight battery tray indicator for KDE Plasma
 A Qt6-based battery tray indicator that works natively on KDE Plasma/Wayland
 without interfering with systemd power management.
 .
 Features:
  - Shows battery percentage with color-coded icon
  - Charging indicator (lightning bolt overlay)
  - Settings dialog with power profile control
  - Configurable notification thresholds
  - Multi-language support (English, Spanish)
